    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1337,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: After 20%: 500x80/100 = 400\nStep 2: After 10%: 400x90/100 = 360\n\n  500 --20%--> 400 --10%--> 360\n\nTRICK:\nSP = MP x (80/100) x (90/100)\n= 500 x 0.72 = 360\nTotal disc = 500-360 = 140 (28%)\nTRAP: 20%+10% is NOT 30%!\n\nAnswer: SP = Rs.360 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
