        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: After 20%: 500x80/100 = 400\nStep 2: After 10%: 400x90/100 = 360\n\n  500 --20%--> 400 --10%--> 360\n\nTRICK:\nSP = MP x (80/100) x (90/100)\n= 500 x 0.72 = 360\nTotal disc = 500-360 = 140 (28%)\nTRAP: 20%+10% is NOT 30%!\n\nAnswer: SP = Rs.360 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
