    },
    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2118,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: TD = (AxRxT)/(100+RT)\n  = (1060x6x1)/106 = Rs.60\nStep 2: BD = (AxRxT)/100\n  = 6360/100 = Rs.63.60\nStep 3: PW = 1060-60 = Rs.1000\n\n  PW=1000 ──[+6% SI]──→ Amount=1060\n  TD=60 (on PW)  vs  BD=63.60 (on Amt)\n\nTRICK:\nPW = Amount x 100/(100+RT)\n= 1060x100/106 = 1000\nTD = Amount - PW = 60\nBD = SI on Amount, BD > TD always!\n\nAnswer: TD = Rs.60, BD = Rs.63.60 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 65,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: TD = (AxRxT)/(100+RT)\n  = (1060x6x1)/106 = Rs.60\nStep 2: BD = (AxRxT)/100\n  = 6360/100 = Rs.63.60\nStep 3: PW = 1060-60 = Rs.1000\n\n  PW=1000 ──[+6% SI]──→ Amount=1060\n  TD=60 (on PW)  vs  BD=63.60 (on Amt)\n\nTRICK:\nPW = Amount x 100/(100+RT)\n= 1060x100/106 = 1000\nTD = Amount - PW = 60\nBD = SI on Amount, BD > TD always!\n\nAnswer: TD = Rs.60, BD = Rs.63.60 ✓",
